title: Tyepyedong
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chinese fusion noodle bar also making rice dishes, soups, and Japanese curry. Primarily meat-based but does offer several clearly marked vegetarian dishes, i.e. noodle with tofu and veggies or rice with tofu and veggies. Freshly cooked and fast service, minimalist decor.
